# ORIG TITLE    Huge handset or smallish tablet? . 
# ORIG CONTENT  Samsung has unveiled its latest – and biggest ever smartphone – the Galaxy Mega. It has a 6.3 inch screen (16 centimetres); though for people with smaller hands there is a 5.8 inch version. The South Koreans keep churning out new models seemingly trying to overwhelm main rival Apple and other smartphone makers with sheer numbers. Some analysts have said it is too big, but what matters is what customers thinks. 
